<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="font-family:spartan">READ TO REMEMBER</h3>
    <p style="color:#9a9a9a;font-size:12px;font-family:sans-serif"><i>This is a daily collection of highlights from your books. You can change the amount of highlights in the app, as well as when and how often you get this email.</i></p>
    <br>
    <h2 style="color:#666666;font-family:spartan; margin-bottom: 30px;">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS</h3>

    <% @flashcards.each do |flashcard| %>

    <span style="font-family:verdana;font-size:12px;color:#686868;font-weight:200;"><b><%= flashcard.source.title %></b></span><br>
    <span style="color:grey;font-family:courier;font-size:12px;">by <%= flashcard.source.author.name %></span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-size:16px;font-family:bookerly;background-color: #DDDDDD;color:#000000;"><%= flashcard.content %></span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <% unless flashcard.my_note.blank? %>
      <span style="color:#9a9a9a;font-size:12px;font-family:sans-serif">Notes</span><br>
      <span style="color:#474545;font-size:15px;font-family:bookerly"><%= "#{flashcard.h_note} - " %><%= flashcard.tag_list %></span>
      <br>
      <br>
    <% end %>
    <br>

    <span style="color:#cccccc;">-----------------------------------------</span>
    <br>
    <br>

    <% end %>
    <br>
    <br>

    <p style="color:#9a9a9a;font-size:12px;font-family:sans-serif">Thanks for stopping by, see you tomorrow,<br>
    Your Read to Remember team ❤️</p>
  </body>
</html>
